wikipedia_page.main:
Vanessa Hobbs (born (1987-05-04)4 May 1987) was a British female artistic gymnast, representing her nation at international competitions.  
She participated at the 2004 Summer Olympics, and the 2003 World Artistic Gymnastics Championships.
